title: #307: Skool's Out Fa'Evah (@JayLarsonComedy)
itunes:title: Skool's Out Fa'Evah with Jay Larson
description: Jay Larson met me at Venice High to talk about our old school days. We sat on the lawn like creeps and talked about high school until we got asked to leave. Great conversation and memories about the most carefree times of our lives. Jay's new special, Me Being Me, is out now at www.JayLarsonComedy.com. Pick it up and get a great laugh while supporting independent artists who make amazing comedy.
